    solution: `${a} × ${b}\n= ${a} × ${Math.floor(b/10)*10} + ${a} × ${b%10}\n= ${a * Math.floor(b/10)*10} + ${a * (b%10)}\n= ${a * b}`,
    hint: `Break ${b} into ${Math.floor(b/10)*10} + ${b%10} and multiply each part.`,
    accept: i => parseInt(i) === a * b };
